                <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
                    <xpath>/Defs/ResearchProjectDef[defName="OG_Imperial_Tech_Weapons_Bolt"]/label</xpath>
                    <value>
                        <label>bolt weapons</label>
                    </value>
                </li>

                <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
                    <xpath>/Defs/ResearchProjectDef[defName="OG_Imperial_Tech_Weapons_Bolt"]/description</xpath>
                    <value>
                        <description>A brutally effieicnt weapon, the bolter fires mass-reactive bolts at its targets, each one a self-propelled missile which explodes with devastating effectiveness after penetrating its target. The fear and awe that bolter fire creates makes it a perfect weapon for shock troops, the hammering thunder of the guns mixing terrifyingly with the dull, wet explosions as flesh is blown apart.</prerequisites>
                    </value>
                </li>

                <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
                    <xpath>/Defs/ResearchProjectDef[defName="OG_Imperial_Tech_Weapons_Bolt"]/prerequisites</xpath>
                    <value>
                        <prerequisites>
                            <li>Fabrication</li>
                            <li>PrecisionRifling</li>
                        </prerequisites>
                    </value>
                </li>

